Didn't have any cilantro, and my proportions were a bit off (used 3 cups of squash, only about a cup of peppers), but still thought this was very tasty. Took hints from some of the other reviewers and added a bit of chopped green onion and some cumin, chili powder, and coriander. Would make this again.

