Made for Thanksgiving. Butternut squash, chives and bell peppers saved from my garden. Had never used Butternut squash and was struggling with it, so I popped it in the microwave for 5 minutes which made cutting it up very easy. No cilantro, so I took advise and used the old bay and brown sugar. Lovely warm fall harvest dish for the holiday.

